The paper deals with the performance comparison and optimization of a cell-free massive MIMO system, which involves wireless communication, signal processing, and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves network infrastructure and distributed access points, which suggests the category cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The optimization problem and the use of geometric programming suggest the category cs.SY (Systems and Control). The use of massive MIMO and the optimization of power allocation suggest the category cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the use of algorithms and optimization techniques suggests the category cs.LG (Machine Learning).
